  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Mode \"Die Together  this mode,call units do not consume resources,But after destrory enemy remain units will be recalled,And reduce the commander's health based on their summoned resources, When commander's health is reset to zero or base has been destroyed,Task failed. So in this mode,you need to configure based on the current enemy to summon evenly matched units,Minimize the number of surviving units after eliminating enemies as much as possible</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Before each wave of enemy refresh, a skill card will be randomly selected</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537650/extras/2d3a388eed0942bc632ab8e93ed5225c.poster.avif?t=1745586157\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537650/extras/2d3a388eed0942bc632ab8e93ed5225c.webm?t=1745586157\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537650/extras/2d3a388eed0942bc632ab8e93ed5225c.mp4?t=1745586157\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After refreshing the enemy,Press the space key to enter deployment mode,Select card and holding LeftMouse button to deploy unit,Press space key again to landing the unit into the scene</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537650/extras/bd98077465e22611e5325ccc3667a4f0.poster.avif?t=1745586157\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537650/extras/bd98077465e22611e5325ccc3667a4f0.webm?t=1745586157\" type=\"video/webm; 